&lt;p&gt;We’ve hired people from McKinsey, from tech, from trading floors — what they share is intellectual rigor, operational drive, speed of execution and a genuine reason for being in this sector.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You likely have &lt;strong&gt;6-12 years of experience, &lt;/strong&gt;including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At least 3 years in strategy consulting or finance/PE, &lt;/strong&gt;including &lt;strong&gt;some at Project Leader or Engagement Manager&lt;/strong&gt; level — or equivalent experience in high-intensity environments that combine &lt;strong&gt;design, finance, and client management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2+ additional years of experience&lt;/strong&gt; in industry, ideally in tech firms, VC-backed start-ups, or impact investing — or bringing relevant content expertise such as agritech, agriscience, climate tech, or carbon sequestration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A university degree in science or engineering &lt;/strong&gt;(preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
